Name: ABORT INSTRUCTIONS
Explanation: THE INSTRUCTION PROVIDED IN PLAIN TEXT FOR ABORT PROCEDURE.

Name: DOWNGRADING OR DECLASSIFICATION INSTRUCTIONS
Explanation: MARKINGS THAT PROVIDE LITERAL GUIDANCE FOR THE DOWNGRADING OR DECLASSIFICATION OF A MESSAGE.

Name: RELEASABILITY
Explanation: RELEASE MARKING INDICATING THE COUNTRIES AND/OR COUNTRY GROUPING TO WHICH THE PRODUCT IS AUTHORISED FOR RELEASE. ACTUAL COMMONLY UNDERSTOOD DESCRIPTION OF THE COUNTRIES OR COUNTRY GROUPINGS (E.G. PARTNERS FOR PEACE ETC).
